<H4>    Mozambique's Chissano Arrives </H4>

<F P=102> MB0905175994 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 
1600 GMT 9 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0905175994 </F>
<F P=104>  Maputo Radio Mozambique Network </F>
