<H3> <TI>   Ambassador to U.S. Announces Plans To Step Down </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ambassador to U.S. Announces Plans To Step Down </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MB0705075494 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 0600 GMT 7 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB0705075494 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] South Africa's ambassador to the United States, Mr. 
Harry Schwarz, has announced in Washington that he is to step 
down as a diplomat. However, he said he was willing to play a 
role in reconstructing South Africa's economy and in shaping the 
final constitution. 

</TEXT>

