<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Fears about pensions in a new dispensation and calls 
for immediate pension pay-outs have resulted in a statement by 
the ANC that it will honor the rights of individual pension fund 
members, and that it has no intention of interfering with these 
funds. The president of the South African Association of 
