<H3> <TI>   RPF Reiterates Position Against French Forces </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    RPF Reiterates Position Against French Forces </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   EA1405151594 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura in French to 
