<H3> <TI>   Government To Send Troops to Rwanda </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government To Send Troops to Rwanda </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AB1705094894 Lagos Radio Nigeria Network in English 0600 GMT 
