<F P=103> MB1805082994 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Justice Minister Dullah Omar has extended indemnity 
from prosecution to 17 May next year. A proclamation to this 
effect has been published in a special government gazette. It 
is the fourth time that the indemnity has been extended, but the 
first time by the new government. 

