<H3> <TI>   Suspects Held for Illegal Demonstration Released </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Suspects Held for Illegal Demonstration Released </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MB1805095394 Mbabane THE TIMES OF SWAZILAND in English 18 
