BFN 

  [Text] The Juba political conference of peace forces 
convened today in the town of Juba and comes as a confirmation 
and reassurance of the peace process and territorial integrity 
within the federal system. The conference also confirms that 
the Sudanese people share a common destiny, reject violence and 
fighting, and that the rebel movement still has the chance to 
return to the mainstream of the homeland so that all the sons of 
the homeland could embark on development and social and economic 
reconstruction. 

