<F P=101> Liberia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Ugandan Troops Deployed in Southeast; Koromah Men Arrested </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ugandan Troops Deployed in Southeast; Koromah Men Arrested </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AB1805173594 Gbarnga Radio ELRL in English 1400 GMT 18 May 94 </F>
